      "writtenOn": "2019-12-05T21:16:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This can run into trouble if multiple threads are active as they can steal each others packets. I.e. thread 1 is waiting for packet 1, and thread 2 is waiting for 2. If thread 2 sees packet 1 they will both lock up.",
      "revId": "6baae5c17227ce0e3233e746fa0710cee5b091e3",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
      "unresolved": true
